Module cloud.piranha.extension.servlet

The Piranha Extension - Servlet module.

This module delivers everything a Servlet container should have available as part of its runtime.

It delivers the following:

  • Annotation scanning support
  • Jakarta Pages support
  • ServletContainerInitializer support
  • TEMPDIR support
  • Web annotations support
  • Web.xml support

  • Packages

    Exports
    Package Description
    cloud.piranha.extension.servlet
    This package contains the default WebApplicationExtension used to configure a web application.
